2 tarah ki baaten krte hain log, inki baaton main mt aana eik kehta hai programming is bht mushkil hai its impossible, doosre kehte hain programming to bht easy hai. Ye dono galat hain bcuz programming mushkil to hai but naa mumkin nhi hai, its doable so just keep going and mehnat krte raho chalte rahoge seekhte rahoge tbhi ye aasaan hoti rahegi. Jo programmers hain wo bhi apki tarah hi hain, nobody is better than anybody ye sirf eik amount of work aur mehnat hai jo koi krke aagay brh jaata hai bcuz zaadaa work zaada mehnat karogay zaada results aayenge.

ham sb saara saara din beth ke lectures sun skte hain lekin agr ham focused nhi hongay, jo seekhrahe hain un skills ko use nhi karengay to bilkul aesa hi hai jese hamne kch nhi seekha so iske liye jitni practice kr skte ho krni paregi bs practice practice and practice, internet pr exercises dhundo apne liye wo solve kro quizzes dhundo solve kro is tarh skills improve hojayengi cheezen aur aasan hojayengi

habit banaane ke liye eik tareeqa ye hai ke calender pr rozaana line draw kro roz ki date pr, is se ye hota hai ke jb ham dekte hain ke 10 din tk kaam kia hai ab aaj bhi kr hi lete hain automatic motivation milti hai. Daily one hour coding krna 100 days tk bht acha hai instead of eik week main eik sth beth jaana aur phr chordena bcuz is tarh habit ban jaati hai sochna nhi parta motivation ki need nhi parti

distractions se bachte raho jitna bach skte ho bcuz wo eik min ki distraction bhi kbhi bht time le leti waapis focus ke sth kaam krne main, mob airplane mode pr lagaado, akele room main bethjao, early morning kaam kro ya late night jahan sukoon miljaye bs distraction ko remove krna hai

kbhi kaam krne ka dil nhi kr raha hota aur dimagh main bhi chal raha hota hai ke consistency hi kamyab banayegi but dil bhi nhi kr raha hota kaam krne ka so phr us waqt eik trick kaam aati hai 20 minutes kaam kro apne brain ko bolo ke sirf 20 minutes kaam karunga uth jaunga is se aap at least beth jaate ho kaam krne aur phr khud hi dil lag jaata hai eik momentum ban jaata hai aur zaada time guzar jaata hai to ye trick follow kr skte hain jb kaam krna bhi ho aur dil bhi naa kare